I '''Thomas Davenport''' (Juliu 9, 1802 â€“ Juliu 6, 1851) metung yang [[pande]] king  [[Vermont]] [[blacksmith]] a menimbentu keng mumunang Americanung [[Direct current|DC]] electrical motor inyang 1834.<ref>[http://chem.ch.huji.ac.il/history/davenport.html Thomas Davenport]</ref>

Tinuknang ya king Forest Dale, metung a puruk malapit keng balen ning [[Brandon, Vermont|Brandon]].

Inyang mumunang ning 1834, menalkus yang battery-powered electric motor. Ginamit ne iti par paganan ne ing metung a malating-modelung kotsi keng mukayad a dake ning ning rili, na iti ing memie dalan para deng [[streetcars]] gumana keng dekurienti.<ref>[http://books.google.com/books?id=dAElGDvk2yUC&pg=PA86&lpg=PA86&dq=%22thomas+davenport%22+streetcar&source=web&ots=h96mutrV5s&sig=q6RnbGmS9lT3is89lLHLmB_-ARw&hl=en&ei=KX2WSYuTL4Oh-gbm7byBCQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&resnum=9&ct=result Electrifying America by David E. Nye, p.86, from Google Books]. Retrieved 14 February 2009.</ref>

Kamne ning kayang asawa [[Emily Davenport|Emily]], ampong colleague king Orange Smalley, Davenport tinggap ne ing mumunang Americanung [[patent]] keng makina dekurienti inyang 1837, U. S. Patent No. 132.<ref>[https://autoguysland.com/check-engine-light/ check engine light]</ref>

